1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,480
Your Majesty.

2
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:31,200
Ning Chen defied the law and executed him.

3
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,359
By law, he must be beheaded.

4
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,319
Your Majesty.

5
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:37,079
I impeach Minister of Rites Ning Ziming.

6
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,519
He failed to discipline his son,

7
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,120
who committed a heinous crime.

8
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,959
He should face the same punishment.

9
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:43,120
Your Majesty.

10
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,319
I impeach Geng Jing of the Imperial Inspectorate.

11
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,239
Ning Chen serves under him.

12
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,640
He allowed his subordinate to commit murder,

13
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,200
slaughtering royal kin. By law, he must be beheaded.

14
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,120
I second the motion.

15
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,519
I second it as well.

16
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:59,159
I second the motion.

17
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,480
This is big trouble.

18
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,239
How did I father such a wretch?

19
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,400
Silence!

20
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:24,479
A pack of fools chasing their own fame.

21
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,520
Can they not see

22
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:27,840
that His Majesty is losing his patience?

23
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:36,759
Ning Chen is already being escorted back to the capital.

24
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,759
Let us wait until he returns to discuss this.

25
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,039
For today,

26
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,439
that will be all.

27
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,560
Your Majesty.

28
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,120
Your Majesty.

29
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,360
Your Majesty.

30
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,080
This old minister has a memorial.

31
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,039
Ning Chen killed the Imperial Uncle.

32
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:53,639
This is an undeniable fact.

33
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:56,240
By law, it warrants Extermination of the Nine Clans.

34
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,960
Fool.

35
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,199
My dear Minister Yu,

36
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:06,680
your service over the years has been great,

37
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,960
but now you are advanced in years.

38
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:11,879
Are your ears failing you?

39
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,360
that you cannot even hear

40
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,400
Our words clearly?

41
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:17,159
If you are unwell,

42
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:20,560
We can let you retire to your hometown.

43
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,199
To think Imperial Father favors Ning Chen

44
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,599
to such an extent.

45
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,240
Old General Chen, Geng Jing,

46
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:29,879
follow Us to the Imperial Study

47
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,560
to discuss this matter.

48
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,199
We obey, Your Majesty.

49
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,840
Last night,

50
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,120
the Empress fainted crying here many times.

51
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,039
Speak, both of you.

52
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,360
What shall We do about Ning Chen?

53
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,759
Your Majesty, a report.

54
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,520
What bastards!

55
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:04,840
To be imperial kin, yet so brutal.

56
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,280
Worse than pigs and dogs.

57
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,599
Those are all Our people!

58
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,000
The bark on nearby trees was stripped clean.

59
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,080
The people were driven to cannibalism.

60
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,120
How dare they be so brazen!

61
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,839
Is Da Xuan still Our Da Xuan?

62
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,279
Ning Chen,

63
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:23,600
even a youth of twenty understands

64
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:26,160
that water can carry a boat, but it can also sink it.

65
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:28,360
Yet they, well-read in the classics,

66
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,639
and feeding on the sovereign's salary,

67
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,720
have the audacity to treat Us this way.

68
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:32,920
They deserve death.

69
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:34,519
Every last one of them deserves death.

70
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,199
Judging by His Majesty's words,

71
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,680
he intends to protect Ning Chen.

72
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,319
Your Majesty.

73
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,839
Though Ning Chen killed the Imperial Uncle,

74
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,439
he had his reasons.

75
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:47,720
His crime does not warrant death.

76
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,240
This old minister agrees.

77
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:52,399
As royal kin by marriage, the Imperial Uncle

78
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,959
should have obeyed the law

79
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,240
and set an example.

80
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:57,160
Instead, he preyed upon the people,

81
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,240
slaughtered the innocent,

82
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,439
and treated lives like dirt.

83
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,800
If the people are left with no way to survive,

84
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:04,079
we all know the consequences.

85
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:06,279
He was driving the people to rebellion.

86
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:07,920
That is treason, Your Majesty.

87
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,360
But the Imperial Uncle

88
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,519
is, after all, the Empress's elder brother.

89
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,839
If We do not execute Ning Chen,

90
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,160
how are We to answer to her?

91
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,759
Unless there is some way

92
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,680
to smooth this matter over.

93
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,720
We cannot think of one.

94
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,600
There's no rush.

95
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,199
We have plenty of time.

96
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:39,720
You may stay here and take your time to think.

97
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,199
Pour the tea.

98
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,000
Enough.

99
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:54,800
Pour.

100
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,560
Father.

101
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,279
Father.

102
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,879
What's happened?

103
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,519
My lord.

104
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,319
What on earth is going on?

105
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,680
Father.

106
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,560
What has upset you so?

107
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,319
That unfilial son!

108
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,279
Ning Chen...

109
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,480
has killed the Imperial Uncle!

110
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:46,879
My lord.

111
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,879
Is that true?

112
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:53,360
Ning Chen killed the Imperial Uncle in Zhenyuan County.

113
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:56,439
He is now being escorted to the capital.

114
00:06:58,399 --> 00:07:00,839
But that is the Empress's elder brother!

115
00:07:04,839 --> 00:07:05,680
This is disastrous.

116
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:08,959
This warrants Extermination of the Nine Clans!

117
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,279
We are all finished.

118
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,079
Ex... Extermination of the Nine Clans?

119
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:18,600
Then...

120
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:22,120
we are included in the nine clans!

121
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,000
That damned Ning Chen!

122
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,399
I should have killed him back then!

123
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:28,720
My lord.

124
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,639
Come with me to find Father.

125
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:31,839
Let's go.

126
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,639
Go. Yes, yes.

127
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:33,600
I already looked for him.

128
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,040
When court was dismissed,

129
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,160
I went to see my father-in-law.

130
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,279
He told us to wait for news at home.

131
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:42,079
But this matter is far too grave.

132
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,439
It involves the Empress herself.

133
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,920
No one can save us now.

134
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:51,040
I fear even your father cannot.

135
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,439
We are all going to die!

136
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:56,800
Not one of us will escape.

137
00:07:59,199 --> 00:07:59,600
Mother!

138
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:00,600
Mother!

139
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:01,959
Father!

140
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:02,959
Father, please think of something!

141
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,639
Call the physician, quickly!

142
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,000
Aren't you the Minister of Rites?

143
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,199
You must be able to find a way!

144
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:06,639
Father!

145
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:07,560
Father!

146
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,279
Father!

147
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,639
I'm still young!

148
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:11,959
I don't want to die, Father!

149
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,720
I don't want to die either, Father!

150
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:16,199
Father!

151
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:21,680
Ninth Princess,

152
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,759
Why don't you sit down

153
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:24,000
and we'll push you instead?

154
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,399
Yes, Ninth Princess.

155
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:26,879
Let's go back to your room.

156
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,439
It's fine. Come push me, quickly.

157
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,440
Hold the rope tight. Slow down!

158
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,840
Brother Crown Prince!

159
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,840
Greetings, Your Highness.

160
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,120
Brother Crown Prince!

161
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:39,799
You're here just in time.

162
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:40,759
Come push me!

163
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,200
Brother Crown Prince,

164
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,080
why do you look so unhappy?

165
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,000
Did Imperial Father scold you again?

166
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,240
It's all right.

167
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:55,799
You're always being scolded by him anyway.

168
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:59,799
Ning Chen stood up for the people of Zhenyuan County

169
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,559
and beheaded the Imperial Uncle.

170
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:03,399
What?

171
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,960
Then Imperial Father should reward Ning Chen.

172
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,399
Let me tell you,

173
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,240
I saw that Imperial Uncle in Mother's palace.

174
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,600
A brainless, fat, and sleazy pig.

175
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:15,960
And a lecher, too.

176
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,360
He harassed one of my maids,

177
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,759
so I gave him a piece of my mind.

178
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,720
It's not as simple as you make it sound.

179
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,240
However bad he was, he was still imperial kin.

180
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,480
Imperial Father should decide his fate.

181
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,720
Ning Chen beheading the Imperial Uncle

182
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:29,639
is a crime warranting Extermination of the Nine Clans.

183
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,159
That serious?

184
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,559
Huai'an,

185
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:37,159
Imperial Father is in a terrible mood right now.

186
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,279
Usually,

187
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,600
Imperial Father dotes on you the most.

188
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,000
Seeing you

189
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,840
might improve his mood a lot.

190
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,000
That's true.

191
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,639
Brother Crown Prince, aren't you coming?

192
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,000
I...

193
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:52,240
I have important matters to attend to.

194
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:53,159
I will take my leave now.

195
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:57,440
Oh, and...

196
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,679
if possible,

197
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,039
put in a good word for Ning Chen.

198
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,399
I don't want to bother with that annoying guy.

199
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,080
That previous cell

200
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,159
was small and gloomy,

201
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,639
damp, and full of rats.

202
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,399
We two brothers

203
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,600
specially moved you to a bigger one.

204
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,320
The bedding is all new.

205
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,240
See that wooden bucket?

206
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,080
We bought it for you to soak your feet.

207
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,440
Ningzi, if you need anything else,

208
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:21,440
just tell us brothers directly.

209
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,200
I'm just afraid we won't get another chance later.

210
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,720
Do you even know how to talk?

211
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,840
What? What chance?

212
00:10:27,799 --> 00:10:28,279
Chenzi,

213
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,720
just stay here for now.

214
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:33,000
Golden Guard Pan has gone to gather information.

215
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,399
There's still a chance.

216
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,440
A chance.

217
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,600
What chance is left?

218
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,000
Actually, Old Feng is right.

219
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,639
The only pity is,

220
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:45,360
I promised to take you both to the Music Bureau.

221
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,720
You'll just have to go by yourselves.

222
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:50,960
My lord, the cell is ready.

223
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:51,840
Go, go, go.

224
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,000
The Old General has arrived.

225
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,279
Greetings, Old General.

226
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:04,799
Old General.

227
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,360
I told you, time and again,

228
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,919
to show the imperial family

229
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,279
the proper respect.

230
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,360
It seems

231
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,080
you only paid lip service,

232
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:20,000
and didn't take it to heart at all.

233
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,919
Every word you said, Old General,

234
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,480
I have kept in my heart.

235
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,440
But if you, Old General,

236
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:29,720
had seen the suffering of the people of Chongzhou,

237
00:11:30,759 --> 00:11:32,840
I believe you would have done the same as I did.

238
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,200
Do you regret it?

239
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,919
I have no regrets.

240
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,679
You've got guts, kid.

241
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:48,080
This is wine and roast chicken from Zhuangyuan Tower.

242
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:52,960
It's the only thing I can do for you now.

243
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,159
You may leave.

244
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:00,960
Yes, sir.

245
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:09,960
Old General, I beg you,

246
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:11,679
save the people of Zhenyuan County.

247
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,919
To root out Chongzhou's corruption,

248
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,960
killing one Imperial Uncle is not enough.

249
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:21,480
The truth is, I've already gathered

250
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,399
evidence against every official in Chongzhou.

251
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,240
But now that I'm trapped in prison,

252
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:27,960
my hands are tied.

253
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,080
I can only beg you, Old General,

254
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:34,320
to restore justice for Chongzhou's people.

255
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,399
You have evidence?

256
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,879
Then why didn't you bring it out sooner?

257
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:42,360
I don't trust anyone in the Imperial Inspectorate.

258
00:12:46,639 --> 00:12:47,960
But I trust you, Old General.

259
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,480
This evidence

260
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,960
concerns the very lives of Chongzhou's people,

261
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,559
and it implicates officials in the capital,

262
00:12:57,679 --> 00:12:59,200
as well as the current Empress.

263
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,159
Old General,

264
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,279
do you dare to take it on?

265
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:11,159
I've spent my whole life on the battlefield.

266
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:13,639
What storms haven't I weathered?

267
00:13:14,279 --> 00:13:16,360
What I lack is a leg,

268
00:13:17,639 --> 00:13:18,879
not courage.

269
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,840
I knew I hadn't misjudged you.

270
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,720
You little brat!

271
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:25,720
Is that how you speak to your elders?

272
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,080
Come, have some chicken.

273
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:34,799
Come, Old General.

274
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:35,399
Here.

275
00:13:35,919 --> 00:13:36,200
Cheers!

276
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,080
You little brat!

277
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:37,799
Cheers!

278
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,720
This time the wine really isn't watered down.

